MCSPI Diag Lib

Files

file  diagLib_mcspi.h
 This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the software test library file of MCSPI. This also contains some related macros.

Detailed Description

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum DiagLib_McspiTestStates

Enum to represent the state of the test.

Enumerator
DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_TIMEOUT 

The test has timedout

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_INVALID_PARAMS 

The test has failed due to invalid parameters

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_BADARGS 

The test has failed due to bad arguments

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_FAIL 

The test has failed in atleast one iteration

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_PASS 

The test has passed in all iterations till now

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_TEST_PENDING 

The test is still running an iteration

enum DiagLib_McspiTransferMode

Enum to select the mode of data transfer in SPI.

Enumerator
DIAGLIB_MCSPI_DMA_MODE 

Select interrupt mode for McSPI

DIAGLIB_MCSPI_POLLED_MODE 

Select polled mode for McSPI

void DiagLibMcspiTestParams_init ( DiagLib_McspiTestParams_t *  testParams)

This API is used for initializing MCSPI test params to default. This API has to be called from app before starting the test.

Parameters
testParamsPointer to structure DiagLib_McspiTestParams_t. Populated with all the default values required for testing of MCSPI configuration.
